OL,3,CChild's foster placement seen as
OL,4,C'inappropriate' before he killed carer
OL,6,FA coroner has said a child who killed
OL,7,Fhis foster carer was placed in her
OL,8,Fhome despite concerns it was
OL,9,F"inappropriate".
OL,11,FMarcia Grant, 60, was run over in her
OL,12,Fown car by a 12-year-old boy she was
OL,13,Fcaring for in the Greenhill area of
OL,14,FSheffield on 5 April 2023.
OL,16,FThe boy - referred to as "child X" -
OL,17,Fwas later sentenced to two years in
OL,18,Fcustody after admitting causing death
OL,19,Fby dangerous driving.
