OL,3,CChild's foster placement seen as
OL,4,C'inappropriate' before he killed carer
OL,6,FAn inquest last month heard "failings"
OL,7,Fby Rotherham Council contributed to
OL,8,FMrs Grant's death.
OL,10,FSouth Yorkshire coroner Marilyn
OL,11,FWhittle has now issued a Prevention of
OL,12,FFuture Deaths Report, saying there is
OL,13,Fa "risk" of further fatalities unless
OL,14,Faction is taken.
OL,16,FThe report raised concerns about a
OL,17,Fshortage of fostering options putting
OL,18,F"significant strain" on the council,
OL,19,Fwhich was responsible for placing the
OL,20,Fboy in care.
