OL,3,CChild's foster placement seen as
OL,4,C'inappropriate' before he killed carer
OL,6,FIt said: "This led to an unsuitable
OL,7,Fplacement being accepted."
OL,9,FThe coroner also said there were
OL,10,Fproblems with documentation and
OL,11,Fcommunication.
OL,13,FShe said: "Both the lack of
OL,14,Fdocumentation recording all the
OL,15,Frelevant risks, failure to complete
OL,16,Fforms and the lack of adequate
OL,17,Fcommunication of the risks in this
OL,18,Fmatter led to a child being placed
OL,19,Fwith a family where numerous
OL,20,Findividuals considered this was an
OL,21,Finappropriate placement."
