OL,3,CChild's foster placement seen as
OL,4,C'inappropriate' before he killed carer
OL,6,FThe inquest heard Mrs Grant and her
OL,7,Fhusband, Delroy, were highly regarded
OL,8,Ffoster carers.
OL,10,FThey were caring for another child,
OL,11,Freferred to as "child Y" when a call
OL,12,Fwent out to all foster carers in the
OL,13,Farea for an emergency placement for
OL,14,Fchild X on 30 March 2023.
OL,16,FThe inquest heard how the couple were
OL,17,Fonly authorised to have one child at a
OL,18,Ftime but volunteered to take him.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/7
