OL,4,C'inappropriate' before he killed carer
OL,6,FMs Whittle said that child X had a
OL,7,Fyouth caution for possessing a knife
OL,8,Fand at times talked about wanting to
OL,9,Fbe part of gang culture, but this
OL,10,Finformation was not included on the
OL,11,Finitial placement referral form,
OL,12,Fmaking it "deficient".
