OL,3,CChild's foster placement seen as
OL,4,C'inappropriate' before he killed carer
OL,6,FShe said Mrs Grant's decision that she
OL,7,Fcould provide him with a short term
OL,8,Fplacement "was made without her full
OL,9,Fknowledge of child X's risks" because
OL,10,Fof "the failings of Rotherham
OL,11,FMetropolitan Borough Council to have
OL,12,Fin place systems and processes to
OL,13,Fensure full details are included and
OL,14,Fup to date forms were used".
OL,16,FThe coroner said the Grants' social
OL,17,Fworker, who was asked for his opinion
OL,18,Fon whether they were a suitable match
OL,19,Ffor child X, was not told about the
OL,20,Fboy's claims he had stabbed people or
OL,21,Fbeen involved in gangs.
